headline: Las Vegas Sands Funds Asian Community Development Council's Health Care, Language Services and Youth Offerings
summary: Las Vegas Sands (NYSE: LVS) has contributed $250,000 through the Sands Cares global community engagement program to the Asian Community Development Council (ACDC) for its Healthy Asian Pacific Islanders (HAPI) Medical Center, API Language Link and developmental programs for high school and college students.
